{"tid":1737573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警於公眾場所播放歌曲 涉侵犯版權","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:06:14.000Z","uid":65166,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"11c5c044cad4dbefa18e5d8202027c950e311b63","tid":1737573,"uid":65166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警涉於非法禁固理大學生時 <br />\n於公眾場所播放含版權歌曲</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n疑事先未先向版權持有人取得所需特許<br />\n由此可見 香港政府及警方毫不尊重版知識產權<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>現呼籲</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">版權持有人可透過民事追討相關損失及民事法律責任</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家幫幫手，傳出去俾版權持有人知道有此權利</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>詳情</strong><br />\n<strong>在公眾場所播放歌曲或音樂需注意事宜</strong><br />\n公開表演、播放或放映版權作品，涉及現時《版權條例》下版權擁有人的「公開表演、播放或放映版權作品」權利。而歌曲的旋律和歌詞以至聲音和視像紀錄，均為條例保護的版權作品。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>本地音樂業界的版權特許機構包括：</strong><br />\n香港作曲家及作詞家協會(<a href=\"http://www.cash.org.hk/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cash.org.hk%2Ftc%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=0740446c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cash.org.hk/tc/</a>) <br />\n香港音像聯盟有限公司(<a href=\"http://www.hkria.com/b5/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkria.com%2Fb5%2Findex.aspx&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=8984db34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkria.com/b5/index.aspx</a>) <br />\n音像版權有限公司(<a href=\"http://www.ppseal.com/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ppseal.com%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=1a138841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ppseal.com/zh-hant/</a>) <br />\n<br />\n<strong>非法禁固理大學生當晚所播放歌曲：</strong><br />\n《那些年》作詞：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九把刀</span></strong>; 作曲：木村充利; 編曲：侯志堅、林冠吟<br />\n《千千闕歌》作詞：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林振強</span></strong>; 作曲：Kohji Makanio<br />\n《追》作詞：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林夕</span></strong>; 作曲：李迪文<br />\n《人海中遇見你》作詞：陳雲鳳/厲曼婷; 作曲：陳揚<br />\n《十面埋伏》作詞：Eric Kwok; 作曲：Eric Kwok<br />\n《告別校園時》作詞：潘源良; 作曲：小栗昌彥<br />\n《真的愛你》作詞：小美(梁美薇); 作曲：黃家駒<br />\n《號角》作詞：鄭國江; 作曲：谷村新司<br />\n《你知道我在等你嗎》作詞：張洪量; 作曲：張洪量<br />\n《真心英雄》作詞：李宗盛; 作曲：李宗盛<br />\n《<del>支那人</del>中國人》作詞：李安修; 作曲：陳耀川 <br />\n《Scotland the brave》<br />\n《Last Christmas》"},{"pid":"17fdbc74f1857614d60d8a5b36efcfeb57c2ef3a","tid":1737573,"uid":65166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"香港人咩都要做吓 求推"},{"pid":"d0828d96d9d079c654416f5564d6920fd048b60e","tid":1737573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"17fdbc74f1857614d60d8a5b36efcfeb57c2ef3a","tid":1737573,"uid":65166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"香港人咩都要做吓 求推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"低能，浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c16a08a0bc5cffae2f3a83daae6ff0355be9d8b","tid":1737573,"uid":41428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f589a59c304b69b68b72d1750a55cc605e7e0bd","tid":1737573,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"3912bec6f751576ff68e5c787340dd07546d1115","tid":1737573,"uid":336090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0828d96d9d079c654416f5564d6920fd048b60e","tid":1737573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"17fdbc74f1857614d60d8a5b36efcfeb57c2ef3a","tid":1737573,"uid":65166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"香港人咩都要做吓 求推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"低能，浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.